That’s what happend to me when I first tried moparscape.

Heres what you do:
There is a link at the top of the page saying “For the Server Status page click here”
click there and at the top of that page it has another link saying “Click here to download MoparScape 3.2.”
after that it will say Download the windows MoparScape 3.2 w/ Aryan installer here or here or here
click the second link, download free, run it, and enjoy
